Version 0.6.0:  Changes made by the cacti-ReportIt Team
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Feature:        Multicolour text within pie charts can be disabled
Feature:        Dynamic FontSize added
Bugfix(#00005): GD function "imageantialias" is only available if bundled gd lib is in use
Bugfix(#00004): Hbar will fail if a title for the y-axis has been defined
Bugfix(#00003): Default maximum ($mx) changed from 0 to 1 to avoid loops in bar, line and hbar chart
Bugfix(#00002): Unable to declare more than one object (Bug#1880343)
Bugfix(#00001): Default header fixed
